; OpenClaw Smart Switch v3.0 - Drill File
; Production Ready Version
; Date: 2026-03-22
; Units: METRIC
; Board Size: 86mm x 86mm
; Mounting Holes: M3, 60mm spacing (standard 86-type)
; Chip: ESP32-WROOM-32D
; Relay: SRD-05VDC-SL-C (Normally Closed)
; 
; Strong-Weak Electrical Separation: X >= 45mm for high voltage

M48
FMAT,2
METRIC,TZ

; ========================================
; Tool Definitions
; ========================================
T1C0.30   ; Via holes (signal)
T2C0.80   ; Signal holes (resistor/capacitor leads)
T3C1.00   ; Component leads (small)
T4C1.50   ; Relay coil pins
T5C2.00   ; Relay contact pins
T6C3.20   ; Terminal block holes
T7C4.00   ; Mounting holes (M3)
T8C0.90   ; Electrolytic capacitor
T9C1.20   ; Button pins

%

G90
G05

